## Acceptance criteria

1. `AsyncQueue` is exported from `@dorkos/relay`
2. Push/consume ordering is correct (FIFO)
3. `complete()` terminates the async iterator cleanly
4. `fail()` causes the async iterator to throw the provided error
5. Values pushed after `complete()` or `fail()` are silently ignored
6. Works with both pre-buffered values and values pushed while a consumer is awaiting
7. All unit tests pass via `pnpm vitest run packages/relay/src/lib/__tests__/async-queue.test.ts`

