The `AdapterRegistry` needs to accept an `AdapterStreamManager` and use it during `deliver()`. When the payload is a StreamEvent and the matched adapter implements `deliverStream()`, the stream manager handles aggregation. Otherwise, the event falls through to `adapter.deliver()`.

